t a RESIST item .<br>As the game stands now you use a shield why?<br> to boost stats your weak in due to class/race  <br>or to boost temp stats becouse the next  mob is known to have a nasty fire spell.<br> Paladins and ok SK's (evil little buggers) can be a great help to a group and a raid but lets face facts we will NEVER be a NEEDED class. <br>why?. easy we cant tank long enough oh we can tank sure  but only for a short time and not all that well in the high end game even counting the new changes its not enough. you will never see a raid called off due to no pally/sk being there. but you see many called off due to no warrior being on hand ,also the clerics in the end game most offten wont even think to heal you and consider it a true waste of mana to spend it on a non-tank /melee. its easyer to rez you then to keep you and the main tank alive .<br> WILL FIXXING BASH HELP.....YES/NO <br> no = sure as damge output goes the more we do the more some one wants us..(WRONG) for bash the more damge you do the more you get of ...NOTHING..  yes nothing  not one single thing ..WHY? becouse bash is a very ify thing will a bash of 10 stop a caster? if the dice are in your favore yes but the same is true for a bash of (1) point . thats called a skill check  you had great skill but the blow was off and didnt land for much damge but it did stop the spell casting &lt;good job&gt; .  <br> yes = bash can help a paladin or SK to be better group mates and raid members, how ?<br> with a higher damge per bash our chance to stun would go up and thats about the best we can ask for? (wrong ) if the delay was lowered then yes we would have a greater chance at the stuns . <br> more damge for bash  bassed in part off the shields AC would allow us a small increase in damge over time but most fights last about 4 to 6 bashes .. not too great a time and even if we hit for 40 to 60 damge thats not any great amount when the mob has 32k HP to start with and the attack is slow enough already that our hate list standing is still where VI wants it to be after all your using a one hander not your high damge 2 hander . but its alot more then just the numbers <br>there is also the mind set of a Knight ( yes i know VI hates us all and has only love in its heart for the necro / monk pukes) after all look what they did to our gods :) <br> the mind set . Knights use shields / Shields are sexy / our shields are a good way to help us get close to some but not all the stats a warrior/ranger has but its not even close to duel wield . if our slower then poured honey bash skill could do more damge it would at least help the player  keep his last few unpulled hairs on his head . <br><br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
